cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Stem Agent: A Pluripotent LLM Agent that Differentiates by Composing Typed Tools"
authors:
  - family-names: Stojiljković
    given-names: Luka
type: software
license: Apache-2.0
repository-code: "https://github.com/lukastojiljkovic/stem-agent"
abstract: >
  A minimal LLM agent that specializes into a domain-specialized agent by
  composing, mutating, and accreting typed tools, with persistent skill
  library across sessions. Methodology anchored on Voyager / AlphaEvolve /
  AFlow / DGM; framing borrowed from developmental biology (stem-cell
  differentiation, neural cellular automata).
